{"tid":868226,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政府擬2020年分階段推行eID數碼個人身份","createTime":"2018-10-19T09:55:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-19T10:09:58.000Z","uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ae00f07fcdb5b0d4b2121e5b605c6f14f4572d17","tid":868226,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T09:55:50.000Z","msg":"創新及科技局局長楊偉雄在一個電台節目表示，政府將計劃在2020年推行數碼個人身份（eID）。<br />\n<br />\n楊偉雄指，eID是要以指紋、聲紋及面部辨識等生物認證方式解鎖，亦經過電腦高度加密，確保資料安全。他表示，政府計劃分階段推行eID，首階段在2020年中或之前供市民申請，亦會將25個常用政府服務連接eID，包括申請公屋、交稅、申請駕駛執照等。<br />\n<br />\n楊偉雄強調，保護市民私隱是一個重要因素，因此市民可以自由選擇是否申請eID，如申請後覺得不安全，也可以取消。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/news/政府擬2020年分階段推行eid數碼個人身份-020517313.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.mobi.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%93%AC2020%E5%B9%B4%E5%88%86%E9%9A%8E%E6%AE%B5%E6%8E%A8%E8%A1%8Ceid%E6%95%B8%E7%A2%BC%E5%80%8B%E4%BA%BA%E8%BA%AB%E4%BB%BD-020517313.html&d=JNKOYaxhaqxPleht%2BagRY5UWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=203f85a3\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/news/政府擬2020年分階段推行eid數碼個人身份-020517313.html</a>"},{"pid":"303710a77f0b826e7509704cbf86ceffcf2129ab","tid":868226,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T09:57:12.000Z","msg":"又可以請少啲公務員<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71f4d2fd5f9aae178096891a7247965656205245","tid":868226,"uid":199145,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T10:06:03.000Z","msg":"唔係好信港共做既encryption<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一個recommend人用IE既政府講data security<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cf621abdc35dcf6d2816e388c1457a54d902315","tid":868226,"uid":65984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T10:09:58.000Z","msg":"其實依家既智能身份証好差咩